# Mission model that pulls `propulsion` in and also extracts its `inner`
# reference up to the parent scope via the `[inner]` extraction block.
# Both `ratio.propulsion` and `g.inner` resolve through the same
# underlying gravity instance.
submodel mid_with_matching as propulsion [inner]

# Performance computed inside `propulsion` should match Earth's gravity.
Earth Mission: result = ratio.propulsion
